These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, musical
House: victorian, farmhouse
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical |
| House     | farmhouse | victorian  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, lawyer
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | eggplant      | kiwi         |
| Job   | writer | lawyer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, blues
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk   |
| Music-Genre       | blues  | r&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
City: hamburg, berlin
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, parkour
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| City   | hamburg  | berlin |
| Sport         | cycling | parkour    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
