.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-9::.
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, begonia
1. the brazilian is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Nationality   | colombian | brazilian |
| Flower           | daffodil    | begonia     |

