.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-10::.
2 different pets are kept: pony, fish
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, hiking
1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |   2    |
| Pet   | pony        | fish    |
| Hobby      | card-games | hiking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-11::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, july
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, teacher
1. the dancer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |
| Birthday   | july | december  |
| Job     | dancer | teacher |

